 easily move, or port, their data to another network. Vanguard Nigeria News Google announced Monday it is shutting down the consumer version of its online social network after fixing a bug exposing private data in as many as 500,000 accounts. October 8, 2018 In "News" Instagram on Thursday added a way for users to easily report deceptive posts at the photo and video-oriented social network owned by Facebook. August 15, 2019 In "News" Facebook on Tuesday introduced "smart lists" that automatically sort friends into categories and prioritize news from those dearest to members of the world's largest online social network. September 13, 2011 In "News"